captions.text:
Hey you!
My name is Thomas "TomSka" Ridgewell.

I'm a twenty-something British
comedy person
and welcome to my YouTube channel!

Hey, guys! Check out my new camera!
[gunshot]
Oh, wait, this isn't a camera.

On my channel, you'll find the three
loves of my life.
First, we have action.
'Cus I really like guns.
and lasers.
and sunglasses.
Cool.
Then we have sketch comedy.

'Cus...this is a comedy channel.
With jokes and stuff.
I'm not gay!
I LOVE IT!
Really, really high brow jokes.

[fart]
Thank you!

Finally, and the reason you probably
found this channel,
We have cartoons!

Mainly my series asdfmovie.
Or A-S-D-F-movie.

Pronounce it however you want,
I just don't care anymore.
Everybody to the flop!
Hello!
But there's also other stuff too.
That's hilarious.

So if that sounds like your kind of thing
then subscribe and stick around for more!
I upload my videos on Fridays...mostly.

Sometimes I get distracted by
video games...aaaahh...

Click here, here or here to check out my
action, comedy or cartoons playlists.
Go on a magical adventure!

Sometimes I try new things and
most of the time they work.

So please don't freak out and unsubscribe
if you see something weird and confusing.

You can handle it.
I believe in you.

Until next time!
TomSka Out.
